# Build artifacts and dependencies
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# Git / GitHub
.git
.gitignore
.github

# IDE / editor
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# Env files (never bake secrets into images)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.template

# Docs
docs/
*.md
!**/README.md

# Tests / fixtures
**/__tests__
**/__snapshots__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
**/test-data
**/fixtures

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Misc tooling not needed at build
mobile/
extensions/
scripts/

# Stale per-service lockfiles (root lockfile is the source of truth)
apis/*/package-lock.json
ui/*/package-lock.json
